OL,3,CBarclay trustees defend their running
OL,4,Cof Sark
OL,6,FTrustees of the Barclay estate in Sark
OL,7,Fsay they "doubt" that a bid to buy
OL,8,Fthem out will be successful.
OL,10,FLast week, the Sark Property Company
OL,11,Fsubmitted a cash bid for the estate -
OL,12,Fwhich includes 80 residential
OL,13,Fdwellings, 20 commercial properties,
OL,14,Ffour hotels, and 139 acres of land.
