OL,3,CBarclay trustees defend their running
OL,4,Cof Sark
OL,6,FChristopher Beaumont, Director of the
OL,7,FSark Property Company and 23rd
OL,8,FSeigneur of Sark who is behind the
OL,9,Fbid, has previously said he wants to
OL,10,F"write a new chapter for the island"
OL,11,Fafter a "difficult period in its
OL,12,Fhistory".
OL,14,FIn a letter to the island's
OL,15,FConseillers dated 10 October, a
OL,16,Ftrustee of the Barclay estate said:
OL,17,F"There is no intention to sell the
OL,18,Festate to the Sark Property Company
OL,19,Funless there is a suitable offer
OL,20,Freceived.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
