OL,3,CBarclay trustees defend their running
OL,4,Cof Sark
OL,6,F"The numbers reported in the Press are
OL,7,Fa fraction of the estate's truth worth
OL,8,Fand we doubt their ability to raise a
OL,9,Fsuitable amount."
OL,11,FThe trustee added: "The estate of Sark
OL,12,Fenjoyed its best year this year ... We
OL,13,Fdoubt there are more places that are
OL,14,Fas well run.
OL,16,F"It is disappointing to see that
OL,17,Fothers, including some of its own
OL,18,F'high profile' residents, value that
OL,19,Fso little."
