OL,3,CBarclay trustees defend their running
OL,4,Cof Sark
OL,6,FChristopher Beaumont has responded by
OL,7,Fsaying:
OL,9,F"Sark Property Company has submitted
OL,10,Fan offer for the estate that
OL,11,Frepresents what we believe is fair
OL,12,Fmarket value plus a premium.
OL,14,F"That offer is valid for 30 days and
OL,15,Fwe will not be commenting on the
OL,16,Fstatus of the bid until that 30-day
OL,17,Fperiod is over.
